      "Redeem our standard quality t-shirt which is made of pure cotton.",
    points: 1000,
  },
  {
    title: "Lightweight Helmet",
    img: "/Helmet.jpg",
    description:
      "Redeem Light Weight helmet which is safe for driving purpose.",
    points: 800,
  },
  {
    title: "A small plant",
